    <p>Flower Power is a cut flower garden located in beautiful, rural Metchosin. We grow a wide selection of perennial and annual flowers, ornamental grasses and restios, flowering shrubs and vines, greenery and filler material.</p>
    <p>Our specialty is meeting all the floral needs of rural/outdoor marriage ceremonies, special occasions and gatherings.  We offer ‘u-pick’ hours for florists and customers who prefer to create their own flower arrangements, as well as beautifully pre-arranged bouquets, centerpieces, floral garlands and wreaths.</p>
